name: Hic, Nunc et la maison volante
description:
The flying house of Hic and Nunc in Anemon's imaginative world - New Year edition
Let's hope for a better life next year. Let's embark on many new and exciting experiences. 2021 isn't the greatest year of the decade, but we're still here alive and well, waiting for 2022 to come. 
Made by puiback using Grease Pencil, Blender
